Introduction
Court Archive is a basketball lifestyle store that offers apparel, accessories, and training-inspired products. The purpose of this assignment was to improve the visual design and customer experience of the Court Archive Shopify storefront. The homepage, product pages, and collection pages were updated to make the brand easier to understand, improve product discovery, and create a more trustworthy and customer-friendly shopping experience.

Homepage Improvements
The Court Archive homepage was improved to communicate the brand’s purpose and target customer more clearly. The main headline, “Built for the ones who stay after,” introduces the store as a basketball lifestyle brand for dedicated athletes. The supporting text explains that Court Archive offers basketball training gear, recovery essentials, and lifestyle products for players who see the game as more than a hobby. The homepage also includes clear calls to action that guide customers toward different products and collections. These changes make the homepage more visually focused, easier to understand, and more connected to the identity of the brand.



