Product Page Improvements
Two product pages were improved: the Sideline Oversized Hoodie and the Archive Mesh Practice Shorts. Both pages were updated with clearer product descriptions and more detailed information about the products’ features, fit, intended use, and care instructions.

The information was organized into shorter sections and bullet points so customers can scan each page quickly. Consistent product images, prices, and formatting also help the product pages appear more professional and trustworthy.

Sideline Oversized Hoodie
The Sideline Oversized Hoodie page was improved with a more detailed description, product features, sizing guidance, care instructions, and clearer product images.

